{
  "stem": "10359.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I was advised by my friends, who finished school there, go for anything-- I don't care-- any kind of, of healing field.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And through somebody that I knew, recommended chiropractor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I figured, I'll try it for a year and see how I like it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And that's how I got involved, and I finished school here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And this was the story.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I went back to Poland, to see my friend Zygmunt Sinawski, the one who put me in the cellar for two, three nights in the theater in November, when I went to get my sister back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I saw him there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's the first time I was in Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was never in Warsaw before, so I don't know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just strictly went to see him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I felt some kind of obligation to visit him, and I felt good about it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I went to see him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, some friends went there for a dedication ceremony, which occurred a couple months ago.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But 70 or 80 people supposedly went there, to dedicate the stone for the-- in the place where they'd killed the [INAUDIBLE], I think.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I just go to temples and high holy days, and all important holy days.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Otherwise, I don't practice, actively, any religious Judaism.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, she [INAUDIBLE] no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I do, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "During the war, I never thought about it, because it became-- it's and esoteric type of a question, that you can't say if you believe in nature or the Holy Spirit or God or some kind of universal intelligence.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, it's all probably means the same.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So if somebody will say, I don't believe in any universal intelligence-- call it God, call it High Spirit-- then it's different.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I do believe in it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't believe that He knows what's going on every minute of my life, or anybody else's life.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But somebody created the universes, and somebody put order in that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I believe that there must be some force that conducts all those things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How I think I survived?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My wife thinks, all the time, that it's luck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There is always the element of luck involved.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But if you just sit-- like some of my friends and other people who are very intelligent people, they sit hoping either God will help them, or something will help them.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or they'll drop a bomb, and everybody will disappear.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't believe in that, so I feel that luck is an important element, if you do something about it to be in the right time and the right place.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's why you have to take papers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You have to have-- like in my case, I had these Polish papers-- establish some kind of communication with people who can help you in the future.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Get some money-- you know what I mean-- so you can put your way through in, in critical situations.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That, to me, is important.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Luck, maybe, comes in someplace in this, into that picture.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I would not say that everything is luck or coincidence, no.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, and escaping here and cultivated friendship with policemen and cultivated friendship with some people all over, just in case something.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wouldn't call it luck.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean that cultivation means it's planning, planning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, after you plan everything, and if you're lucky, your planning works out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But if you-- if you're lucky, if you don't plan anything, you'll be hanged by the luck.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that my definition of luck in my case.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't know who I.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wasn't Mark Grinims, I was Skrbacki.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was hiding.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was justified to do anything, just to save my life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, I didn't do any-- I didn't fight.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was just sitting like an idiot, watching the prisoners cutting down trees in the woods.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, it was just looking at them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They shouldn't escape, whatever.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I didn't do anything actively, or I was in the army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I never thought about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would never thought about it to begin with.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think they would even try to escape, because they needed some food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So this wasn't anything that came into my mind at that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At that time, I had to play the role, and try to, to make everything believable as it is, so I can survive and Dorothy could survive.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Without me, she couldn't survive at that time, because she needed me in the hospital, and after the hospital.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I had to maintain all that image, and do the best I can, just to survive.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We know each other since childhood-- I mean, from teenage years, from the town.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
